{
  "stem": "10587.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It got to the point where the kapos would, would take-- make us carry out dead bodies, and prop them up, and hold on to them so they can get more pieces of bread, the kapos.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because they counted the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and it was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was-- actually, it, it seems like it was cold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because it must've been like maybe [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] August, I would say, roughly, and maybe because the-- you were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That didn't help, either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So then they would call, and who wants seconds?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So when I saw that the people were pushing, you know, and they would-- and the kapos that would dish out the food would take the ladle and split your head with it, and the blood on the ladle.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then they dunked it in again and, and poured the next.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I realized right away that if I do that, I'll be killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, I'm not going to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my father said, you know, same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this went on for a few weeks like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What about the smells?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Did you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the smell was horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and the, the conditions were appall-- appalling conditions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You-- because you, you, you didn't change your clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't, you couldn't take a shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't wash.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You, you [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lived like an animal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they packed you in, in those [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bunks, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which were, like, maybe 10 to a bunk, you know, 10 to a bunk.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- my father got very sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And his, his feet would started to swell.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then his head was swelling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was usually [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the beginning of a total deterioration from-- when, when I saw this, I, I was very upset.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [CRYING] one day, we went, we went to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said-- because he could hardly walk at that time-- they said, all the sick people, you don't have to work today.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You don't have to go to work today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they-- they-- we marched out of the-- to the work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he-- when I came back in the evening, he was gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was-- I, I saw him that morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said goodbye to him, told him I'll see you later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, and I never saw-- [CRYING] never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father, [CRYING] I remember, when I was a little boy, he used to carry my younger brother and, and wait for Shabbat to be over.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He used to sing to him [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- I remember when I came back, [CRYING] and all these wonderful things that my father-- it's like a total void.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And all of a sudden, I didn't have anyone to, to tell me anything, to give me advice, and to protect me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I couldn't protect him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] and Auschwitz was such a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] horrible place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You, you-- if you, if you had to go to the bathroom, first of all, the facilities were like one barrack, they were taken.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, and there were holes, you know, where you would sit down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so when I saw what's happening, I used to try to go to the bathroom during daylight time, during working hours.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because at nighttime, some of the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] guards from the towers would take potshot at you and kill people to-- just going to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the only thing I said, how do I get out of this hell hole?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] so-- We're going to change the reel, OK?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to stop and change the reel.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
